{
 "name": "RPlog_Morrison_and_Joir",
 "title": "Morrison and Joir",
 "summary": "In Plaxton's Fountain Square, a tense moment over drawn blasters among Caspar marines is defused as the cold Imperial Joir arrives and joins his associates Troy, Azya, Webb, Kaein, and others. The scene then shifts to a private booth where Joir meets with Morrison, the urbane director of the CSA's ruthless Security Police, marked by the Black Sun tattoo on his wrist. Over cigarettes and mineral water, the two power-players spar diplomatically about CSA intentions in the Empire-aligned Mutanda system, Morrison's interest in an abandoned orbital station, and the murky background of his rising subordinate Aldog. Each guards his information as a form of power, and the meeting ends with mutual wariness and an open door to future dealings.",
